Program: Discovery
Title: Codex Alimentarius Commission
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxnl
Last Broadcast Date: 27 July 2000
The Codex Alimentarius Commission, food safety scheme. The Rome-based organisation is a joint operation between the UN and the World Health Organisation and sets international food standards and tries to maintain fair practices. The programme looks at the work Codex does and how successful it has been. Show less